<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Making his way through the streets he is greeted by Halas's residents. The moods and tones are hushed everywhere he goes and people have only superficial things to say about the weather, Giants, Darkelves etc. More often then not he is recieved by half smiles and sad eyes. Quetly he walks the streets to the main gates of Keep MacLear. Its banner flying limp in the calm air, odd for this time of year. Out front Gretta Terrillom is selling her wares. She steps back offering a bow to the old shaman. Her spirit not quite right since she wandered back from the moon after the Vampyre Keep was sieged.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>The two guards at the gate step forward to question Ravnanger as if he was a stranger. Young and new to the job they soon recognize Ravnanger for who he is.  One saluting one bowing they quietly watch him pass to the large doors of the Great Hall. The Hall warm and full of good smells from the kitchen is a sight for sore eyes. It is obvious many MacLears have been about recently.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em> Tired from his journey Ravnanger finds his way to his room. The Dark tanned purple Orcskin and ivory door sticks a bit then swings wide. His room dusty and spartan he packs his few things into a trunk unceremoniously. Heafting the trunk onto his shoulder he heads past the Chieftesses office to his new room. Opening the Large wood and Iron door Ravnanger sets down his things over by a large bureau. Once more he marvels at Lanadena's good taste in appointing their room with craftsmanship and finerys. Lady's mantle scents the room. The sound of someone straining down the hall piques his curiousity and he investigates. Three doors down he finds Oli straining to move some large crates. Crates Marked Property of Engel. Lending a hand he hears the story of the Gnomish ship and how this room came ot be filled with crates of equipment. Oli offers tae buy Rav a drink for his help but he is weary and saddened and  thus returns to his room</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Locking his spears in their racks and hanging his Wyvrn hide tunic and Jarseth leggings on a hook Ravnanger looks about for places to put his things. Dressing in a fine woven shirt Lana Had left out for him and wraping his Dark tartan about his shoulder and waist he fills a mug of ale and pushes his chair closer to the Hearth. His feet up and his drink barely touched he falls asleep.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em> One by one Leather'n Padding make their way onto his lap. Gwen the sharp haze panther kitten leaps to the top of the chair and settles between the chair and Rav's shoulders. The chorus of the three kittens purring is only broken by the snaaps and crackles of the fire...and the odd snore from Ravnanger. Gwen only half sleeping watches though almost closed eyelids and may in fact look annoyed her sisters are so soundly asleep. Her paw tensing and unsheathing of her claws the only betrayal of her mood.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://p203.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=1794.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://p203.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=1794.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://p203.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1794.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://p203.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=1794.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://p203.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.threadControl?topicID=1794.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://p203.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1794.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a hr